{"title":"- Clase VGI-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/- Clase VGI-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Clase\\NVGI","guid":"4jgE79UCHJ7IygGUvkuRrg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Enfoque\\NGeriátrico:","guid":"UeeZj3QOSDJffn4dVuJ56w","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Siglo XX: ↗ grandes avances para prolongar la expectativa de vida.","guid":"p9lWC6iZx6vGK5pDrcCaBw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Siglo XXI: Desafío ↗ que la vida sea de calidad.","guid":"O1NvXrdBNwYIZrhFjzUGCg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Calidad de vida en el adulto\\Nmayor afectada por:","guid":"UlRcGmwZVXUFTvvqLbEL_A","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Discapacidad (proceso continuo\\Nque puede ser intervenido):","guid":"EKAER0_QvDxgP3qN-2u_1w","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Estresor → Impedimento → Dificultad en el funcionamiento →\\NRestricción en la actividad diaria → Dependencia → Postración.","guid":"8xzD3RZl0OdQMylKMcUCbA","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"Cambios fisiológicos\\Ndel envejecimiento:","guid":"4LjocLHZP1aV6ZIQy_McgQ","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"↓ Adaptabilidad","guid":"QhrLZU6Gr4Ggg-6T3bSMNg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"↓ Reservas fisiológicas","guid":"bPRuPeccfRHcAGgJl271fA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"↑ Vulnerabilidad a enfermedades crónicas y degenerativas","guid":"Cm0wQwWxnMbb-YZm8k6yJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"4","text":"Influencia: factores genéticos, estilo de vida, factores socioeconómicos","guid":"HWdMN72WVZLwOeJHFJtdVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"↑ Riesgo de pasar de independencia a incapacidad","guid":"Y0-7zlzOxqC7A0rXySmxkQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"80 años: 3+ enfermedades crónicas (comorbilidades)","guid":"7PhK4KxozpIk-R6CH_VJlg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"¿Cómo distinguir un adulto\\Nmayor saludable?","guid":"TX2tpLyF-_6RFpDkhAharA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Funcionalidad:","guid":"jYFp3I4NR11RlUHEzXdiQw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Principal marcador de\\Nbienestar en la persona mayor","guid":"FM7iw7RwxEfBYmUujbzm4A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Salud en la vejez:","guid":"qOZrMZ5HxYsrbJgdncGz-g","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Una persona mayor sana enfrenta los procesos de cambio con\\Nadecuada funcionalidad y satisfacción personal (calidad de vida).","guid":"9i12HPQ64LNCt_V4LM5qng","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Salud según la enfermedad:","guid":"BoWGn4--flOsD3TAuvuvdg","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Indicadores: Morbilidad / Mortalidad.","guid":"9jPl57iwITPAj8Gs30U0vA","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"Salud según la funcionalidad:","guid":"tqg2g1tLIxj9l3MpaLvaTA","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Indicador: Independencia funcional (capacidad de llevar a cabo actividades del diario vivir).","guid":"GSrtiQ1dsLqYe4Fs5M6t1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Funcionalidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Capacidad de realizar acciones del diario vivir con independencia y autonomía.","guid":"XtOsLAcK1mNXaF_iaG-ifg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Independencia: Capacidad de realizar funciones diarias sin ayuda.","guid":"gQkus34oGZSSe63Z-dYtUA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Autonomía: Capacidad de tomar decisiones y afrontar sus consecuencias.","guid":"Yz55vOASd12alYjsljl8hQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"¿Cuáles son las actividades\\Ndel diario vivir?","guid":"b5mDT-GpdXA2Maui6l7S1A","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Actividades básicas de la\\Nvida diaria (ABVD):","guid":"LPWrqs-4PfcQft6E_ayncw","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Destinadas al autocuidado: comer, vestirse,\\Nhigiene, caminar, bañarse, usar el inodoro.","guid":"l558dTq-F5FZbrpqVvBQpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Actividades instrumentales de\\Nla vida diaria (AIVD):","guid":"Rkdsa49kWh6ix1c_BrxJtw","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Tareas más complejas que requieren inteligencia práctica: usar el teléfono, ir a\\Nlugares lejanos, comprar, tareas del hogar, tomar medicamentos, manejar dinero.","guid":"ihVhdL4IJ7r9QadOv1ls6g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"23","text":"¿Cómo medir la funcionalidad\\Nde un individuo?","guid":"MXYCjsdrWslY5WGhEDwyDQ","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Escalas de\\Nfuncionalidad:","guid":"4ILfskAbWSXYSxuV8TGj-w","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Índice de Katz","guid":"mBn8kKAtLbK9805me5B8tw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Índice de Barthel","guid":"5GW6ZnMmDwzBUPWQTreMWg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Escala de Lawton y Brody","guid":"lliXxIUGC-EE4HHYa5zOPQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Escala de Pfeffer","guid":"DejATuwL0TnCVathBh111A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"23","text":"¿Qué factores\\Nprotectores existen?","guid":"kL8kFnSVlPSsH-FPBZFnAA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"23","text":"¿Qué factores de riesgo de\\Npérdida funcional conoce?","guid":"96iWtS7FPFEU7bWqfwMyHA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"23","text":"¿Podemos intervenir en la\\Nmantención de la funcionalidad?","guid":"JaoJ3179oHatvOkf1JklJA","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Pérdida de funcionalidad:\\NProceso progresivo.","guid":"2pwfAw7UfEyKQQUR5wndMA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Es prevenible, retrasable y aliviable.","guid":"gTQgL3-KO5TblpZ_aYjbQw","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Prevención de pérdida funcional","guid":"9u8ZJCbLclfFN3zCn-pflg","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Recuperar la funcionalidad se vuelve más difícil cuanto más avanzado está el proceso.","guid":"sW-k70D3tnTDYQIjfk9i3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Requiere un instrumento integral:","guid":"Vb2BHgmgDqautuApWQhjVQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Biomédico","guid":"lMsihIbkcqL23m8XMRm8zA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"Mental","guid":"v16K4EQHJihNXo7mFiTeHw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"Social","guid":"yZY4TatMB4TbBkJ2Lrceng","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"Funcional","guid":"_0Px98Qu4QCWZ70qIKCuHg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Valoración geriátrica integral\\N(VGI)","guid":"d9IpcoCT3k6R5WA7oF2jnA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Instrumento diagnostico y terapéutico","guid":"-un1IesMYfkOjTZzUYqB-Q","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Objetivo:","guid":"nhe7mJtiXJF0ocWFYFoqMA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Identifica deterioro funcional, cognitivo/psíquico,\\Nsocial/ambiental y biomédico no evidente.","guid":"kvSM8-9Spulsu1IYDpYEJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Características","guid":"0bt5C0ZNi5n-7DT1f3zkKA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Multidisciplinario.","guid":"GF_bNsgXeUyNIUJxZlXH8A","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Mayor utilidad en paciente frágil.","guid":"XaILGG7I1eOFKeU7RtfCFg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Permite generar un plan de tratamiento coordinado.","guid":"Mx7MV9WcObYTQe6JAqvbFw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"Siempre incluir a la familia o cuidador.","guid":"JAyXOYB127bVr8Tb2xlhFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"50","text":"Indicaciones\\Nde VGI:","guid":"t1WjGhMtkPu57PE1MuNGQg","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Edad avanzada (>85 años).","guid":"x_dBAWoIupmuELo23yyZBQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Alto índice de comorbilidad.","guid":"5s2WpPDm_JpoACpdo8bD6g","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"Síndromes geriátricos.","guid":"aDaz-eDP1HL0CgxxEWIBNA","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"Consideración de institucionalización.","guid":"yIEJ-4XAkKGHKazPfvkLiA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"59","text":"Otros modelos:","guid":"yvDixzyYnakGsv_ixRK6Bw","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Patologías específicas: Fractura de cadera, UPP, NAC a repetición.","guid":"8R9ufX705A_wq_ul3PmMMw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"50","text":"Exclusión\\Nde la VGI:","guid":"UmwVlbdVLB1baqnsyVdx6A","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Paciente terminal","guid":"bvzwA3WlheDH6pf9UE8E1A","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Demencia severa","guid":"qhGcw4UJmXhfzn8tRnDVtA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"Dependencia funcional severa","guid":"GJ1z6i8RHZ2Gi7BXaKZRtQ","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"Institucionalización","guid":"LmB86ubNJE18nslx-vt20A","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"50","text":"Equipo\\Ninterdisciplinario:","guid":"VwCIKv38ygaTljFV2l7-1A","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Medico/enfermera/AS","guid":"8jtpaVJOF3UjzoSuD5UJoQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"TO, nutricionista, kinesiólogo, dentista, psicólogo, FA.","guid":"Ec1G7QN9Bigfsj2CorDk3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"50","text":"Componentes\\Nesenciales de la VGI:","guid":"Ufjj7LGXUnAiHArwlMqEgA","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"Funcionalidad","guid":"sXg7oz5eY0ds75SQbjNdaw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Movilidad, marcha, balance, fuerza muscular","guid":"KrrcuTtEjdKnwMDB-v6Q6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"Síndromes\\Ngeriátricos:","guid":"Gj1it7tR2lDitb2h0hyjjA","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Caídas","guid":"D9RK8tgJRy4uXdu9Bzy2ew","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"Fragilidad","guid":"lfouiZ3XRx63cXevcSH1Xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"74","text":"Fármacos","guid":"9VylptgCuiTKfdhHD-RkuA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"74","text":"Cognición","guid":"KSqkErU4xft-LwOn6UemqA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"74","text":"Esfera anímica","guid":"quYoZ15jg2InyHtq7GuCBg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"74","text":"Valoración social","guid":"ACGjqObk8NRDJm6mrx2kNA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"74","text":"Deseos y directrices anticipadas del paciente.","guid":"kcTyRdZ5G6N_k3it4TnlKg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Funcionalidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"El estado funcional tiene valor pronóstico.","guid":"tM1FU-Oeqo_DnaJSH8sWKA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"Actividades básicas de la vida diaria: Solo el 10% de la población comunitaria está afectada.","guid":"tqupcM8-sSTc_lvjS_U0GQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"Actividades instrumentales de la vida diaria: 20% de adultos mayores tiene dificultades;\\Ndistinguir entre causas físicas y cognitivas.","guid":"3_GbpP8-n6OAP_Uqicj4QQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"Actividades avanzadas: Ocupacionales, recreativas, viajes.","guid":"HW46Syw5L6WfaE-DNuY3cg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"Movilidad:","guid":"HBqsio2a-JUI_bdjnNDZyw","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Marcha:","guid":"a7D_kgQ1kO9UypL5PsKzyA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Se correlaciona con riesgo de caída, sarcopenia,  fragilidad y morbimortalidad","guid":"zvPxpJLCHMlyQt6NcOqMmQ","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Largo del paso, alto del paso, balance, continuidad.","guid":"J1l8XUPaLNMDoddn0qqAkg","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"Velocidad de marcha: Test de caminata de 4m, corte <0,8 m/s.","guid":"KDTDh433iof6u5oYp0yVdA","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"85","text":"Balance:","guid":"B-PCoPt_7hKMn1EkW7lbLg","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Test de pararse (tándem) por 10 segundos. SPPB <8/12 puntos.","guid":"yECy7jXSf3J64zTiO91xyA","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"85","text":"Fuerza muscular:","guid":"pkKSh6VryhUQzi2qHVGJOw","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Test de levantarse 5 veces sin usar brazos.","guid":"ZuDpdyCsp2ctCpMqSmb_LQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Time up and go: Combinación de marcha y fuerza, corte 20 segundos.","guid":"kkkks_6oMIaEiz3GJQWNBA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación del\\Nriesgo de caídas:","guid":"DTxJAHe9PewigmzAraQVfw","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Prevalencia:","guid":"tPmPvDIME7tV_o3RwjHx8g","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"30-40% entre 65-80 años.","guid":"Oy2RqUfZ5DmhwXWAza1P3Q","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"50% en mayores de 80 años se caen al año,\\Npredisponiéndolos a declive funcional.","guid":"FucxkahUYsqwORwu7saVfg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"10% caen con daño; 50% pérdida funcional, 2% fallece, 50% postcaída.","guid":"r0p1Ebgbx2NOnyCPQiy9Gw","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"Evaluación:","guid":"fv1ON7VoaIReekPEtVhXlw","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Historia de caídas (OR 2.3).","guid":"sZUno__CrEj0gLRptdnk-Q","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Hipotensión ortostática, visual, revisión de fármacos (OR 1.6).","guid":"YQjAUOfBBqIqcXvWf6Kgug","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Evaluación de pies, balance, fuerza del tren inferior.","guid":"y1YB8s54NvVcZVBn2-BkrA","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Seguridad en el hogar (checklists CDC).","guid":"PYIOEgWswJlN5flJEjdozw","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"100","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"vOumM1E4TH9Va7KcRLTSbQ","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Multicomponente (RR 0.7), ejercicio y Tai Chi (RR 0.6/0.7),\\Nmodificaciones ambientales (RR 0.64).","guid":"OmY8DAyh6_M93RoDmq24TA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Fragilidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Definición: Estado de baja reserva fisiológica, mayor vulnerabilidad ante estresores\\N(homeoestenosis).","guid":"9AL5x__lZ66b4cksz9VyPg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Prevalencia: 7% en la comunidad, 60% en fractura de cadera.","guid":"3G96XMMi8dAaXy1X0OyVAw","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"En Chile: 14% >60 años y 24% >80 años.","guid":"mVIluuQetvCmizs53OLLSg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Asociación: Mayor morbimortalidad, estancia hospitalaria, dependencia funcional.","guid":"EvfWVzLqZ-3S4w0jC_Y6tg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"Estudios:","guid":"JFSfgo-xWlPwMkwm-eSqqA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Makary et al.: OR 2.5 de complicaciones, OR 20.48 para desfuncionalización.","guid":"iBG4X2TA_NABf3-EfdlOZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"112","text":"Medidas de\\Nfragilidad:","guid":"bCaQOM70464EX1Q0Sg1Fhg","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Gold standard: VGI, Criterios de Fried, Frailty Index.","guid":"3SHFyjONlZ7fiu4w1u47Og","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Marcadores subrogados:\\NAUC 0.775.","guid":"iKKPqoqecXgcpomSKR7-dA","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"Velocidad de marcha: <0.8 m/s (S/E 99/64%).","guid":"En7ymhzDyIRyLVNc1F5z0A","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Fuerza prensil: VN 27 en hombres, 16 en mujeres.","guid":"X4wuTWhXbjughjOLiQf74Q","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"Hemoglobina, Albúmina.","guid":"u3mNshuOyULprfZlCRh3ag","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"Estado nutricional: MNA.","guid":"aQoZUcUK0CUhisZGIkJkxA","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"Área muscular del Psoas (coreclier.com).","guid":"B16B_JXY6FOUVAKWx8K3Kg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"112","text":"Escalas de\\Nfragilidad:","guid":"x3CiRHxwoC3FtstrqywkYg","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Clinical Frailty Scale (CFS).","guid":"5XEYKADq28A19xmyyySGvQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Criterios de Fried.","guid":"FrCJnC9BU8O3jJ6N5Lt2tQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"0","text":"Fármacos:","guid":"_BFgaOKOjKCgTAJy3npbQg","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"Deben ser prioridad en la evaluación geriátrica.","guid":"zZEarabgEp-3EEo4f4x6dg","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"Fármacos potencialmente\\Ninapropiados:","guid":"pgwVM0lq_0Nr7KPMHLMd3w","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"APS 20%.","guid":"tObMWnv2U9NSm7AAqGfwKA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"Atención secundaria 30%.","guid":"A9560GYckMZf8Z7rznQSkw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"Institucionalizados 70%.","guid":"4OYi8i8aa7fpQlBOIS5Z-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"130","text":"Omisión de\\Nfármacos:","guid":"Rx4xFBfr7yF7Ek85OdRnqQ","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"APS 20%.","guid":"nxrQFNaloxQDvJ28HW7wxQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"Secundaria 60%.","guid":"kAung1IwYKk8G9gzKyrfzg","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"Institucionalizados 40%.","guid":"Yfc07C8507qdFMswyeTqAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"130","text":"Prevalencia de polifarmacia en Chile (>4 fármacos): 36%.","guid":"6dSZY0ushNzfBOHhwH3GmA","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"130","text":"Hasta el 25% de las hospitalizaciones de adultos mayores están\\Nrelacionadas con reacciones adversas a medicamentos.","guid":"xcjGLf9-AJK-_Vy5NZ-jgA","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"130","text":"Prescripción\\Napropiada:","guid":"h-84at4EScJUlCMkkAuVnQ","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Balance favorable riesgo/beneficio.","guid":"OzPah9TiNzFKPtBxB9wB5g","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Evidencia clara de utilidad.","guid":"1aZix2-hdQpLwz0u2F4Z-Q","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Buena tolerancia.","guid":"1tE8StV0ePPbU0eTRa4B1Q","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"Costo.","guid":"cUzkyZS0hbibM7fJ35CITA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"142","text":"Time lag to benefit.","guid":"mB5ipuoJfIwxhoFcvTTaew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Cognición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Test de\\Nscreening:","guid":"BlUZ2Vv-wyYmA71ggOwaWQ","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"MMSE: Punto de corte 23/30 (menos preciso para deterioro cognitivo leve).","guid":"e-ynCJAeaOq6w1TTWJl2Jg","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"MoCA: Punto de corte 26/30 (interferido por nivel educativo).","guid":"fedlyJA7S5-r8a0lgX6J7g","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"Identifican individuos para evaluación profunda,\\Npero no diagnostican etiología.","guid":"C3ohgnasNyXoY0dnUJXNzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"Test neuropsicológico formal: Orienta a etiología.","guid":"AZW8Rj8elgAtM30axtyM-A","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"148","text":"Entrevista clínica:","guid":"qwThWIP3DycjJ7dD2kUAKw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Observa aspectos cognitivos y conductuales.","guid":"dBz-Q_BBR7xete22l15HpA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"Depende de edad, nivel educativo, funcionalidad\\Npremórbida, medicamentos, etc.","guid":"d2vBS6635e_3PtmB28yoqQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"Alteración cognitiva → demencia si impide AIVD.","guid":"wbEG29RjoKbbd4sIactfSA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"0","text":"Esfera\\Nanímica/insomnio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Test de las 2\\Npreguntas:","guid":"hR7EIg5J2R5gc_iHs1nL9Q","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"¿Se ha sentido bajoneado, deprimido o\\Ndesesperanzado en el último mes?","guid":"oSXOpXdYAlRo6s3lG1Z1-g","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"¿Ha estado menos interesado en\\Nhacer cosas en el último mes?","guid":"HEBfBV4TM1_j9lQWMpZo8A","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"S/E: 97/67% (ambulatorio y sin deterioro cognitivo).","guid":"z-lCJqn9ehMaU9zLox0HwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"GDS Yesavage de\\N5 preguntas:","guid":"wAa917PJbs_HJM-IsPegcQ","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"2/5 sugiere depresión.","guid":"X5RagFiw417uZYzOjIQnEQ","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"S/E: 94/81% (ambulatorio y hospitalizado).","guid":"vDl6EwiM4WsvuAOftzfI4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"158","text":"PHQ 9:","guid":"xSOMGuMY8Bp_lHT94uVZvA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Fácil de aplicar, cubre todos los criterios DSM-5.","guid":"xLcgbr5sDOjoyU8RbSIUHQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"S/E: 88/88% (ambulatorio sin deterioro cognitivo).","guid":"ej9sFLNHnOGdzMTbP5od-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"158","text":"Escala de\\NCornell:","guid":"YWVZlpF3ZggrjaEch2pGdw","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"Útil en pacientes con deterioro cognitivo.","guid":"cXPedQeMpNWG2kwZv6KOyA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"S/E: 90/75%.","guid":"gNYf5HaFmZNBhR-TAKhfMg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Valoración social\\Ny ambiental:","guid":"5KIBKjAvtH1-hqdwOotGbg","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Identifica la necesidad de asistencia en la red\\Nsocial y su impacto en la condición clínica.","guid":"d1Fl3U6kwJsg-zEDZVZpiw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"Incluye evaluación de sobrecarga del cuidador (Zarit).","guid":"ABCDluCOWr7RBBQE16vLIg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"Relevante para el plan de alta\\Nhospitalaria y cuidados transicionales.","guid":"NDWhom426NJHTUZ5A9lIZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación pronóstica y\\Nmetas del paciente:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Importancia: Evaluar el pronóstico permite guiar decisiones clínicas\\N(ofrecer o no medidas preventivas o aliviar consecuencias a largo plazo).","guid":"iwCbkguJNel6mNoMVevt-w","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Impacto del pronóstico en\\Ndecisiones clínicas:","guid":"W0n_rApuZiX3iSvGCc0xrQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"<6 semanas: Depresión, fin de vida.","guid":"_ddvc08SgsKAZy_iG3MHcA","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"<3 meses: Hiperlipidemia, metástasis espinales.","guid":"goRnEvF-HBi75YLXxvnaUw","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"<6 meses: Derivación a hospicio.","guid":"W_3bY3tbPKi6MHwS9Ts6gQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"<2 años: Control glicémico, prevención en diabetes.","guid":"k4lZHDYbwyhbbsER1gXhhw","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"<5 años: Hipertensión, reemplazo valvular.","guid":"YYYH43bKv0X5GooHOEsJYw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"<8 años: Cribado de cáncer, complicaciones microvasculares en diabetes.","guid":"UxanbL-IzHZMUP9w3XalDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"176","text":"Herramientas de\\Nevaluación pronóstica:","guid":"QAufeQ5-1sc5CyRNRmDBUA","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"Calculadoras online: eprognosis.ucsf.edu.","guid":"gf1-BjMA01pJbhl_4LgXGA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"Tablas de sobrevida según edad, sexo y raza\\N(no consideran condiciones clínicas).","guid":"gDvyD-_DceKYOGeKXx8zcA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"0","text":"Proceso\\Nclínico:","guid":"Jl7lxAcnhcfyTPWvXkiWYw","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Recolección de información (idealmente multidisciplinaria).","guid":"cGJJ1bihNl2bAMquOIMTng","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Discusión de equipo.","guid":"qNRL0uU8bdDCKgiyIXfIIA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"Desarrollo de plan de intervención.","guid":"AvXNmHZHFw1r4GCnGLax4Q","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"Implementación.","guid":"kStLQmZGqOTUo-gFOsHsDQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"188","text":"Evaluación de respuesta.","guid":"oUNlP5XYUFANE9CLQbcWhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"0","text":"Metas de\\Ncuidado:","guid":"SctS_Hw9l17WuHN0ogQJnA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"Definir metas del cuidado una vez realizado el diagnóstico.","guid":"kntFxt0k7JA8nQb4Vz9oJg","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"Metas habituales\\Ndel paciente:","guid":"2UgpVzYUEZJt8qKy9MBUhg","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Recuperación de alguna funcionalidad.","guid":"0rKhkD0lUQTfhmdrdszTYA","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"Recuperación social (ej. retomar actividades sociales).","guid":"k4k62Y9Jd8TJ7JIWFsNXnQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"Importante: Incorporar los deseos y expectativas del paciente.","guid":"Gs9KEGVde7dqvOPMge87IA","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"194","text":"Metas\\Nindividualizadas:","guid":"G4rNcT34ym9tLZsSaM94kQ","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"Adultos mayores sanos: Aproximación tradicional orientada a la enfermedad (medicina interna).","guid":"sXT8TqKe9GwVpv3WxVzy3w","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"Pacientes frágiles o con\\Nexpectativa de vida baja:","guid":"cFSAliqiKHGA1MNn_MXUJg","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"Orientación a control de síntomas, mejora de funcionalidad,\\Nmovilidad o roles sociales.","guid":"fkZ4yfTqkPhg88EWAbu0xA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"El tratamiento puede limitarse a lo que el paciente considere apropiado.","guid":"VE2Ow7m-PQMjpM2o259ttw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"0","text":"Modelos\\Nde VGI","guid":"swqYpuaBej1fKs_SZBC5gA","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"\\\\*Con evidencia\\Na favor\\\\*","guid":"v6VwL3G0KQFnY5OL9Ianfg","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"Valoración\\Ndomiciliaria:","guid":"6NG54J0nCkzZXnFGiw0aFg","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"Modelo preventivo.","guid":"2iDfPlQ4TTQDhSzopAy_WA","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"Metaanálisis: Efectividad en evitar pérdida de\\Nfuncionalidad y reducir mortalidad.","guid":"59hlVC4AvwzAkWGyTUULCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"Unidades geriátricas\\Nagudas:","guid":"HTf1XErrGDu78Gd8MXOUyw","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"Equipo especializado a cargo.","guid":"Wk2JQPmRMoyPIyVr3Z2WFQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"Metaanálisis: Mejora funcional (OR 1.75), evitar institucionalización (OR 0.64),\\Nreducir mortalidad (OR 0.72).","guid":"ufPRZa7dk-vV4h1ECzIt7A","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"Más efectivas que equipos móviles.","guid":"TOqSnZYDpImUEtCtDWJ60A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"205","text":"Discutibles:","guid":"XRXJD9lrF3qsCR1sLMFKAw","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"Valoración peri-egreso hospitalario.","guid":"nrSHhlodoP_jwZf7r6cjkQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"Consulta geriátrica\\Nambulatoria/APS:","guid":"jPGQRDcGHuy2jj6cfrSmyg","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"Evidencia conflictiva en\\Noutcomes relevantes.","guid":"rh96VOrLdL6-EnpnYjO5tg","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"214","text":"IC geriátrica\\Nhospitalaria:","guid":"XsZkZQVk7IguxuiJjR-0Pw","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"Metaanálisis sin efecto en funcionalidad,\\Ntasa de readmisión o tiempos de estadía.","guid":"pis5igpyHyK0czJxNMfJ8g","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"Excepción: Cuidado conjunto con geriatra en ortogeriatría (menos\\Ncomplicaciones, mortalidad, delirio, y mejor tiempo de estadía).","guid":"_UDjPyhizTKjiLCR9FL3CQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"0","text":"Conclusiones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"El principal marcador de bienestar en la persona mayor es la funcionalidad.","guid":"jbXNxtkJII354ElhEhFxIA","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"La pérdida progresiva de la funcionalidad → discapacidad y ↑ morbi-mortalidad.","guid":"xE0IlcF9oOYrImSjxshxWA","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"221","text":"La funcionalidad se mide mediante escalas de ABVD y AIVD.","guid":"dXtG-hPLySbYXsgEKpH0mQ","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"221","text":"Es posible prevenir la pérdida funcional.","guid":"dqmSuphfe8qp668G-XrhUA","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"221","text":"Es posible recuperar la pérdida funcional con terapia en muchos casos\\N(potencial de recuperación).","guid":"iD39vcHChPZhJjHSVTZISQ","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"221","text":"La VGI es un instrumento diagnóstico-terapéutico que permite identificar\\Nriesgos/causas de pérdida funcional y proponer un plan terapéutico.","guid":"XMmhqwS8rn89i6OhYHPp8g","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":227,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría","filename":"- Clase VGI-2024","id":"map_904","resolved_references":[]}